Invocation Name: big ninety five point seven
des:
Big 95.7 launches as the only Classic Hits formatted radio station in Tri-Cities, playing the greatest hits of the 80’s 90’s and beyond from artists like Hall & Oats, 
Madonna, Phil Collins, Duran Duran, Mariah Carey, Michael Jackson, Journey, Whitney Houston, Billy Joel and Prince with a 100,000 watt signal that covers the entire Tri-Cities and Walla Walla marketplace as well as the cities of Hermiston, Umatilla and Pendleton. The reach of Big 95.7 is massive, reaching the entire region, from Moses Lake, Clarkston, Toppenish and beyond.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
